# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PortPane by ShackDesk — RSA Public Key
# Project  : https://github.com/Computer-Tsu/shackdesk-portpane
# Author   : Mark McDow (N4TEK) — My Computer Guru LLC
# Owner    : My Computer Guru LLC
#
# PURPOSE
# This file contains the RSA public key used by PortPane to verify:
#   1. License key signatures  — validates commercial license keys offline
#   2. Update manifest signatures — verifies update packages before installing
#
# SAFE TO SHARE — THIS IS A PUBLIC KEY
# This is the PUBLIC half of an RSA key pair. It is intentionally included
# in the repository and distributed with the application. Sharing a public key
# is normal and expected — it cannot be used to generate or forge license keys.
#
# CANNOT BE USED TO GENERATE LICENSE KEYS
# Only the PRIVATE key (which is never stored in this repository, never shared,
# and held only by My Computer Guru LLC) can generate valid license signatures.
# Possession of this public key gives you no ability to create, forge, or modify
# license keys. It can only verify that a key was signed by the private key.
#
# FINGERPRINT (SHA-256 of public key)
# [PLACEHOLDER — will be filled in when the RSA key pair is generated]
# Example format: AB:CD:EF:01:23:45:67:89:AB:CD:EF:01:23:45:67:89:
#                 AB:CD:EF:01:23:45:67:89:AB:CD:EF:01:23:45:67:89:AB
#
# KEY DETAILS
# Algorithm  : RSA
# Key size   : 2048 bits
# Format     : PEM (Privacy Enhanced Mail, Base64-encoded DER)
# Usage      : Signature verification only (not encryption)
#
# STATUS: PLACEHOLDER
# A real RSA key pair has not yet been generated for this project.
# This file will be updated before the v1.0 stable release.
# The private key will never appear in this repository.
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

-----BEGIN PUBLIC KEY-----
[PLACEHOLDER — replace with actual RSA 2048-bit public key in PEM format]
[Generate with: openssl genpkey -algorithm RSA -pkeyopt rsa_keygen_bits:2048]
[Export public: openssl rsa -pubout -in private.pem -out portpane-public.pem]
[Keep private.pem SECRET — never commit it to the repository]
-----END PUBLIC KEY-----
